    "text": "Public Service Pays Off Act\n\nThis bill requires the Department of Education to incrementally cancel a percentage of the obligation to repay the balance on eligible Federal Direct Loans for a borrower who, while employed in public service,\u00a0makes qualifying payments for 2, 4, 6, 8, and 10 years."
